sections.heading: companies; violations; general penalty
sections.text: Any company or person who knowingly violates any provision of this chapter for which no penalty is provided, shall be guilty of a Class III misdemeanor.SourceLaws 1913, c. 154, ยง 155, p. 472;R.S.1913, ยง 3292;Laws 1919, c. 190, tit. V, art. XI, ยง 20, p. 653;C.S.
